OL,5,G2235 DJ Carey - The Dodger
OL,6,     FAt the pinnacle of his fame DJ's
OL,7,     Fmarriage ends and the media pursue
OL,8,     Fhim relentlessly. Soon, questions
OL,9,     Fabout his health and finances
OL,10,     Fbecome unavoidable.
OL,11,G2340 Unforgotten
OL,12,     FVarious suspects start to come out
OL,13,     Fof the woodwork as Gerard Cooper's
OL,14,     Fextreme right wing views become
OL,15,     Fmore apparent to the police.
OL,16,G0035 Sherwood
OL,17,     FThe Sparrows are on the warpath
OL,18,     Fand Ann is the target. The various
OL,19,     Fthreads of the investigation
OL,20,     Ffinally come together, as the
OL,21,     Fcommunity looks to the future.
